{"id": "1415698182041637068", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "429271179615010816", "author_name": "mevius8354", "author_bot": false, "content": "はぇー私も参考にします", "timestamp": "2025-09-11T13:59:08.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1415700442557448325", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "745174421219704852", "author_name": "argonova", "author_bot": false, "content": "今日からはじめる者です、完全無知です\nストーリー進行重視、キャラ指定無し、無課金予定（必要に応じて微課金）です\n見るべきスレッドや、知るべき情報があれば教えていただきたいです", "timestamp": "2025-09-11T14:08:07.948000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1415701310677975070", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "913332610221101097", "author_name": "angel___0808", "author_bot": false, "content": "ガチャプランとかは知っておくと楽なのかな でもパニグレメインなら限定は引かない（虹石）、シルバーコアは貯蓄が丸そうですね", "timestamp": "2025-09-11T14:11:34.924000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1415702846980100148", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "913332610221101097", "author_name": "angel___0808", "author_bot": false, "content": "恒常は超次元優先、ストーリーの章終わりごと・プレイヤーレベルの上昇（5か10の倍数）あたりで急に生えてくる課金パックは効率がいいです ただし2-3日で消えます", "timestamp": "2025-09-11T14:17:41.207000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1415703036411772938", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "745174421219704852", "author_name": "argonova", "author_bot": false, "content": "開始直後に進行不能ぽくなる落とし穴系要素はなしですね？", "timestamp": "2025-09-11T14:18:26.371000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1415703156452495513", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "745174421219704852", "author_name": "argonova", "author_bot": false, "content": "詰み要素というか、ストーリー進行重視なので……", "timestamp": "2025-09-11T14:18:54.991000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1415703380143247451", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "913332610221101097", "author_name": "angel___0808", "author_bot": false, "content": "ないですね！ただ1章の最後に難所があるので 育成で上から殴るのが早いんですけどまっとうに勝負するとなると見据えて育成しないとですかね", "timestamp": "2025-09-11T14:19:48.323000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
